{"tid":1374131,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"就夢遊一事 小弟有小小建議","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:30:24.000Z","uid":249460,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b98d584975427a5661ae47ea073a6b68df8c7cb9","tid":1374131,"uid":249460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:19:47.000Z","msg":"有好多人分唔清「走」同「退」嘅意思<br />\n「退」即係向後退<br />\n「走」即係散水<br />\n一有催淚煙，好多人大叫「走」（事實上，應該係「退」），結果有班人真係走咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我建議</span></span><br />\n「退」就叫「退」<br />\n「走」先叫「走」<br />\n同埋<br />\n「退」或「走」個陣<br />\n請大叫「1，2，1，2」，而唔係叫口號<br />\n咁先有秩序<br />\n始於大家行路速度同步伐不一<br />\n無秩序好容易人踩人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同請正皮<br />\n第一次出post<br />\n有咩得罪請多多包涵<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"44c05797844021b22e6d840701d344f2ef996c8a","tid":1374131,"uid":249460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c95c3882e7455bc685f4d5a3a2abb9922f69596","tid":1374131,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"前線退不嬲窗嗌1212"},{"pid":"cdd59a33ba6b2e60a12893a7b8cf1bd4bcdd4496","tid":1374131,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c95c3882e7455bc685f4d5a3a2abb9922f69596","tid":1374131,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"前線退不嬲窗嗌1212"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:23:34.000Z","msg":"會*"},{"pid":"5c513ba2586dd32e3a300a4719b2f42a72029409","tid":1374131,"uid":249460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c95c3882e7455bc685f4d5a3a2abb9922f69596","tid":1374131,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"前線退不嬲窗嗌1212"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:23:4